   *=============================================================*
                   Magical ARMOURS in Avenir Domain
   *=============================================================*


Scarlet-gold set                (~Avenir/common/dark/obj/worm_armor)
Creator:        Boriska
Desc:           Scarlet-gold helmet, robe and shield.
Stats:          AC = 30, AC mods are 5, -2, -3
Special:        Low weight and volume, acid and fire resistance.
Magic:          enchantment
Props:          OBJ_M_NO_BUY
Cloned by:      Can be made by player (miniquest)
Difficulty:     Requires tough monster to be killed in order to make it.

Spider Amulet:                   (~Avenir/common/port/obj/uw_amulet )
Creator:        Glinda, Cirion
Desc:           Black amulet
Stats:          AC = 1, no AC mods
Special:        Gives MAGIC_I_RES_POISON of 30 (additive) to the wearer
Magic:          life
Props:          MAGIC_AM_MAGIC, OBJ_I_IS_MAGIC_ARMOUR, MAGIC_AM_ID_INFO
Cloned by:      ~Avenir/common/port/uw11
Difficulty:     Difficult, requires defeating a difficult monster in a
                deadly area, and even then only appears 50% of the time

Golden Gauntlets:                (~Avenir/common/port/obj/uw_gauntlets )
Creator:        Glinda, Cirion
Desc:           Pair of golden gauntlets
Stats:          AC = 17, AC mods 1, 2, -3
Special:        Gives the prop LIVE_I_QUICKNESS to the wearer, based on
                his dex. It is also increased if the player is currently
                resistant to death or earth. Those resistant to life, air,
                or who are undead, can not wear them. The range of increase
                is 35 - 60.
Magic:          life, air
Props:          MAGIC_AM_MAGIC, OBJ_I_IS_MAGIC_ARMOUR, MAGIC_AM_ID_INFO
Cloned by:      ~Avenir/common/port/uw11
Difficulty:     Difficult, requires defeating a difficult monster in a
                deadly area, and even then only appears 50% of the time


Ruby-eyed snake ring:         (~Avenir/common/bazaar/Obj/worn/jband )
Creator:        Ilyian / Cirion
Desc:           Ruby-eyed snake ring
Stats:          AC = 3, no AC mods
Special:        Conveys the following resistances to the wearer:
                    MAGIC_I_RES_FIRE:  15 (additive)
                    MAGIC_I_RES_AIR:    8 (additive)
                    MAGIC_I_RES_MAGIC:  3 (non-additive)
Magic:          water, enchantment, earth
Props:          MAGIC_AM_MAGIC, OBJ_I_IS_MAGIC_ARMOUR, MAGIC_AM_ID_INFO
Cloned by:      ~Avenir/common/bazaar/NPCS/jadestone
Where:          ~Avenir/common/bazaar/extr/hill
Difficulty:     Fairly difficult - must kill Jadestone Doll to get it

Coral necklace:              (~Avenir/common/dead/obj/necklace )
Creator:        Cirion
Desc:           Long coral necklace
Stats:          AC = 18, no AM
Special:        Conveys the following resistances to the wearer:
                  MAGIC_I_RES_WATER: 55 (additive)
                  MAGIC_I_RES_EARTH: 60 (additive)
                  MAGIC_I_RES_MAGIC:  8 (non-additive)
Magic:          life, enchantment
Props:          MAGIC_AM_MAGIC, OBJ_I_IS_MAGIC_ARMOUR, MAGIC_AM_ID_INFO,
                MAGIC_I_RES_WATER, MAGIC_I_RES_EARTH
Cloned by:      ~Avenir/common/dead/mon/naiad
Where:          ~Avenir/common/dead/marsh/marsh_hill
Difficulty:     Indirect reward for a large (50k) quest

