Cahor's Amulet: ( ~Avenir/common/zigg/obj/camulet )
Creator:        Lucius, Apr 2007
Desc:           engraved chromatic amulet
Stats:          AC = 1, no AC mods
Special:        Detects when illusion magic is used on wearer,
                aids in the detection of invisible people/items
                Will also grant see_invis when proper command used.
Magic:          Illusion / Counter-Illusion (mystery)
Props:          MAGIC_AM_MAGIC, OBJ_I_IS_MAGIC_ARMOUR, MAGIC_AM_ID_INFO
Cloned by:      ~Avenir/common/zigg/mon/rynal.c
Difficulty:     Difficult, requires defeating a difficult monster that
                grows stronger each time a player defeats him.

thief_gloves    /d/Avenir/common/port/obj/thief_gloves
Creator:        Ibun, summer 2007
Desc:           pair of black leather gloves
Stats:          AC 2;
Magic:          none
Props:          MAGIC_AM_MAGIC, MAGIC_AM_ID_INFO
Cloned by:      /d/Avenir/common/port/mon/thief
Where:          /d/Avenir/common/port
Difficulty:     Moderate. Have to kill 4 npcs to get it.
Special:        Adds 10 to SS_PICK_POCKET.
                Allows to distract opponents to lower their
                awareness up to max 40 (single opps) or max 20
                numeral opps.
                Together with shadow_cloak (see below)
                they form a set that add bonuses.

shadow_cloak    /d/Avenir/common/port/obj/shadow_cloak
Creator:        Ibun, summer 2007
Desc:           dull gray cloak
Stats:          AC 3;
Magic:          none
Props:          MAGIC_AM_MAGIC, MAGIC_AM_ID_INFO
Cloned by:      /d/Avenir/common/port/mon/thief2
Where:          /d/Avenir/common/port
Difficulty:     Moderate. Nonbouncable opponent.
Special:        Adds 10 to SS_HIDE.
                Together with thief_gloves (see above)
                they form a set that add bonuses.
Setbonus:       Wearing both gloves and cloak adds +10 to SS_SNEAK
                and SS_KNIFE.
                Wearing both items allows the player to hide in the
                shadows. An action that raises SS_HIDE by 100 for
                this hide. NOTE the hide in shadows is severely
                limited due to the terrain demands, TERRAIN_SHADOWS,
                is a must. TERRAIN LIMIT REMOVE - TERRAINS ARE ONLY
		SPORADICALLY APPLIED AND NOT A RELIABLE DETERMINER



